title: Rechargeable Motion Sensor Light( Indoor and Outdoor)
description:
• About Product:-

  

 Only work under the darkness or weak light. It is highly suggested to attach to the wall, fridge or place parallel to the human body. not suggest to put them like under the cabinet, not enough space to sense body. but it is ok to do so if you can guarantee there is enough space to sense the human body

The USB on the left or right side will strengthen the sensitivity when you attach the magnet sticker.

No need battery

USB Rechargeable for use.

More economic and cheaper in a long run

Charging mode(if support): USB charging style: Warm white / Cool White Charging time(if support): 2 hours

What’s in the box:- 1 x Motion Sensing Light (Battery include), 1 x USB Charging adapter
